data.description: Welcome to a modern haven of comfort and style in the heart of Boise. This beautifully designed residence boasts an open-concept living area, a gourmet kitchen, and a serene master suite on the main level. Upstairs, find versatile spaces for work, and play, and two additional bedrooms. Step outside to a private backyard with a covered patio, perfect for outdoor gatherings. Conveniently located near schools, parks, and amenities, this is your chance to experience the best of Boise living. Don't miss out—schedule your showing today at 9691 W Sageberry Dr. Open House This Weekend! Saturday & Sunday 12 to 3 PM
